                %a.multi{href:"http://fahan.tas.edu.au"} Reading and Leads 2011
                %a.multi{href:"http://fahan.tas.edu.au"} Glastonbury 2011
            %section
                %p During my time at Picture, we were tasked to create templates with reusable content modules to aid Music Journalists in the field during major UK music festivals.
                %p These templates were designed to run with the BBC's 'Old Stack.' They were in no way powered by a CMS so markup had to be simple to allow the content teams to make quick edits.
            %figure
                %img{src: "images/mmft.png"}
            %section
                %p Custom skinning of components was done for each festival.
                %p With the release of the BBC's new stack 'Forge' these sites have been superceded by a far superior event CMS known as Evis.
            %figure
                %img{src: "images/mmft2.png"}
